’s what we found.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-types-of-free-seo-tools\">Types of Free SEO Tools</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-best-free-tools-for-website-seo\">Best Free SEO Tools for Website SEO</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-best-free-keyword-research-tools\">Best Free Keyword Research Tools</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-backlink-checkers-and-link-building\">Backlink Checkers and Link Building</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-best-free-site-speed-checkers\">Best Free Site Speed Checkers</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-best-free-analytics-tools\">Best Free Analytics Tools</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-resources-on-seo-tools\">Resources on SEO Tools</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-types-of-free-seo-tools\">Types of Free SEO Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve categorized our best free SEO tools into website SEO, keyword research, backlink analysis and link-building, speed tools, and analytics tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep in mind that the tools we’ve reviewed come in 1 of 3 forms:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Chrome extensions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Web-based tools</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Downloadable plugins</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ll start with website SEO tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-free-tools-for-website-seo\">Best Free SEO Tools for Website SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-aioseo-analyzer-fast-seo-checks\">1. <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/aioseo-analyzer/gdmkcblhddhhfejpfbjomilpgpbpjhhg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">AIOSEO Analyzer</a>: Fast SEO Checks</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Speed up SEO checks with this free Chrome extension from the All in One SEO team. It works on both unpublished <em>and</em> published web pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-1024x907.png\" alt=\"aioseo analyzer overview\" class=\"wp-image-234411\" style=\"width:612px;height:543px\" width=\"612\" height=\"543\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-1024x907.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-300x266.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-768x680.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-600x532.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-68x60.png 68w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1-102x90.png 102w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-overview-1.png 1323w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO checks include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Title and meta description</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Internal and external links</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Headings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Image SEO</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Schema markup</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Social media OG tags</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Canonical URLs</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sitemap and Robots.txt</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The compact display of headings (h-tags) provides a fast way to check for logical structure.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-1024x917.png\" alt=\"aioseo analyzer headings tab\" class=\"wp-image-234412\" style=\"width:608px;height:544px\" width=\"608\" height=\"544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-1024x917.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-300x269.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-768x688.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-600x537.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-67x60.png 67w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab-101x90.png 101w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-headings-tab.png 1319w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can easily find out if images on a page are missing alt tags.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-1024x947.png\" alt=\"aioseo analyzer image tab\" class=\"wp-image-234414\" style=\"width:612px;height:566px\" width=\"612\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-1024x947.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-300x278.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-768x710.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-600x555.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-65x60.png 65w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo-97x90.png 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-image-seo.png 1320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>We used the Analyzer to check image SEO on a blog post and found 15 images with no alt tags.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Analyzer also provides a quick schema check. If schema is on your page, the associated types and properties will be displayed in a scrollable list.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-1024x980.png\" alt=\"aioseo analyzer schema check\" class=\"wp-image-234416\" style=\"width:627px;height:600px\" width=\"627\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-1024x980.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-300x287.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-768x735.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-600x574.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-63x60.png 63w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found-94x90.png 94w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-analyzer-schema-found.png 1313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 627px) 100vw, 627px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All of these checks are important to ensure that your website is optimized for search engines and can be easily found by potential customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-seo-analyzer-by-all-in-one-seo-web-based-tool\">2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-analyzer/\">SEO Analyzer</a> by All in One SEO: Web-Based Tool</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a URL and get a detailed site audit with this free SEO Analyzer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-1024x481.png\" alt=\"aioseo seo analyzer\" class=\"wp-image-234418\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-1024x481.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-768x361.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-600x282.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer-192x90.png 192w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-seo-analyzer.png 1184w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The overall site score gives you an idea of how much improvement is needed. Analyzed items are grouped by</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Critical issues</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recommended fixes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Good Results</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on any of those items to get details.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"505\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-1024x505.png\" alt=\"aioseo seo analyzer interface\" class=\"wp-image-234419\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-1024x505.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-768x378.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-1536x757.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-2048x1009.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-600x296.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-122x60.png 122w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/seo-analyzer-critical-issues-183x90.png 183w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Clicking on Critical Issues revealed 3 items. Click the arrows at the right to get details on the item.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The report covers basic SEO, advanced SEO issues, and performance and security checks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s a satisfying amount of detail here. Marketers could use it to prepare for sales meetings or discovery meetings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll also get the option to download the report as a PDF.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin-everything-you-need-to-rank-higher\">3. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</a>: Everything You Need to Rank Higher</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to improve your SEO without hiring a marketer? All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is a 5-star plugin over 3 million people use to optimize their WordPress websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo best free seo tools\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin analyzes your web pages and provides a checklist (and guidance) for improvement. Readability recommendations are included too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"507\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-1024x507.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo sidebar\" class=\"wp-image-233289\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-1024x507.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-300x149.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-768x381.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-1536x761.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-2048x1015.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-600x297.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-121x60.jpg 121w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/aioseo-general-settings-182x90.jpg 182w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The price for the premium AIOSEO plugins starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing\">$49.50/year</a>. But you can get the Lite version for <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free on WordPress.org</a>. This is one of the best free SEO tools available. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Try it out, then upgrade at any time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some of the benefits of the free version.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Improve SEO with an action checklist for each web page</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Get found by search engines with auto-generated RSS and XML sitemaps</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Increase click-throughs by using the title tag and meta description checkers.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Control how your pages appear on social media.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Maximize click-throughs from search engines with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippets</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO analysis tool for site audits and recommendations</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\">ChatGPT integration</a> to generate titles and descriptions</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Upgrade to the Basic or Pro version to get local SEO tools, the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\">ChatGPT integration</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\">Redirection Manager</a>, and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\">Link Assistant</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-free-keyword-research-tools\">Best Free Keyword Research Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword research is the starting point for content that ranks high. And these free tools will help you pick relevant keywords or find out who’s already ranking for them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-free-google-keyword-research-tools\">4. Free Google Keyword Research Tools</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google provides some excellent ways to get keyword and ranking data, and some of it is hidden in plain sight.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are our picks.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Chrome Incognito</strong> and <strong>Google Search</strong>: It’s possible to plan content that ranks using these 2 resources. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-secrets-to-grow-revenue/#aioseo-1-produce-high-quality-content-that-aligns-with-search-intent\">Here’s how</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Google Keyword Planner</strong>: Create a Google Ads account to use this tool. Check out <a href=\"https://support.google.com/google-ads/answer/7337243\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google’s instructions for the planner</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"><strong>Google Trends</strong></a>: Get ideas from trending topics. Interest is displayed on a relative scale.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-ahrefs-keyword-generator-get-keyword-ideas\">5. <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/keyword-generator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs Keyword Generator</a>: Get Keyword Ideas</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter a keyword into the Ahrefs Keyword Generator to get 100 related keyword ideas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ten of the 100 will display a related Keyword Difficulty score. These scores make it possible to pick keywords that are easy to rank for.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"884\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-1024x884.png\" alt=\"ahrefs keyword generator\" class=\"wp-image-234420\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-1024x884.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-300x259.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-768x663.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-1536x1326.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-2048x1768.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-600x518.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-70x60.png 70w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-keyword-generator-104x90.png 104w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll need to sign up for Ahrefs to access more than 10 Keyword Difficulty scores per search. But you’ll get search volume numbers for all 100/per search keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs pricing for the paid version starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$99/month</a>. It’s well worth it, and you can cancel at any time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-6-answersocrates-discover-questions-people-are-asking\">6. <a href=\"https://answersocrates.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">AnswerSocrates</a>: Discover Questions People Are Asking</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter a topic into AnswerSocrates, and you’ll get organized lists of questions searchers have.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"442\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-1024x442.png\" alt=\"answersocrates example\" class=\"wp-image-234422\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-1024x442.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-300x130.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-768x332.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-1536x663.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-2048x884.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-600x259.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-139x60.png 139w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answersocrates-dashboard-208x90.png 208w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It pulls some of this data from People Also Ask questions in Google Search. The rest of the data comes from Google Suggest and Google Trends.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The homepage of AnswerSocrates also displays data on trending topics.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-answerthepublic-find-topics-and-related-questions\">7. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/answerthepublic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">AnswerThePublic</a>: Find Topics and Related Questions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Add 1 or 2 words to AnswerThePublic, and it’ll generate a series of related topics and questions searchers have.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This information is pulled from Google’s autocomplete data.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The circular display of the data is novel but hard to read on laptop screens. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-1024x646.jpg\" alt=\"answerthepublic interface\" class=\"wp-image-234423\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-1024x646.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-300x189.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-768x485.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-1536x969.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-2048x1292.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-600x379.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-95x60.jpg 95w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/answerthepublic-keyword-research-143x90.jpg 143w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AnswerThePublic has turned this into a <a href=\"https://answerthepublic.com/pages/features\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">sales pitch</a> for their paid version: &#8220;Our visualization is nice. But prolonged use may lead to neck injury if you need to analyse data for more than 5 mins.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The paid version allows you to export data to a CSV file.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AnswerThePublic provides 3 searches a day for free, but you’ll need to sign up for more data. Plans start at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/answerthepublic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$9/month</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-8-exploding-topics-get-in-on-trends-early\">8. <a href=\"https://explodingtopics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Exploding Topics</a>: Get in on Trends Early</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This exciting project, launched by Brian Dean of Backlinko, provides keywords that are spiking exponentially in traffic or are on the cusp of doing so.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-1024x478.png\" alt=\"exploding topics examples\" class=\"wp-image-234425\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-1024x478.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-768x359.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-129x60.png 129w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/exploding-topics.png 1418w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: 2 examples of exploding topics.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The goal is to unearth long-term growth trends, not temporary fads.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll need a paid plan to get access to all exploding topics. Pricing starts at <a href=\"https://explodingtopics.com/pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$39/month</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-9-alsoasked-discover-relevant-questions\">9. <a href=\"https://alsoasked.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">AlsoAsked</a>: Discover Relevant Questions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>AlsoAsked is a unique tool that lets you explore People Also Ask questions by geography.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter a keyword, and results are displayed in an interactive mind map.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version provides a handful of searches a day. Paid plans begin at <a href=\"https://alsoasked.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$15/month</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"501\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-1024x501.jpg\" alt=\"alsoasked seo tool\" class=\"wp-image-234426\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-1024x501.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-300x147.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-768x376.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-1536x752.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-2048x1002.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-600x294.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-123x60.jpg 123w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/alsoasked-keyword-research-interface-184x90.jpg 184w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-10-ubersuggest-keyword-research-tool\">10. <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">UberSuggest</a>: Keyword Research Tool</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Like AlsoAsked, Ubersuggest imposes a tight limit on free searches: you only get 3 daily. So treat this tool more like a free trial with no time limit.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"671\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-1024x671.png\" alt=\"ubersuggest keyword tool\" class=\"wp-image-234428\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-1024x671.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-300x197.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-768x503.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-1536x1006.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-2048x1342.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-600x393.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-92x60.png 92w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-keyword-overview-137x90.png 137w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: Close-up of the Ubersuggest interface.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Semrush</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs</a>, this tool provides keyword ideas, content ideas, keyword difficulty score, CPC, backlinks data, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing starts at <a href=\"https://app.neilpatel.com/en/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$29/month</a> for 1 domain.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-11-ahrefs-serp-checker-ranking-research\">11. <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/serp-checker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs SERP Checker</a>: Ranking Research</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter a keyword into the Ahrefs SERP Checker and see who ranks in the<strong> top 4 positions</strong> in Google Search.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sign up for a $99/month account to get more data. Or use Chrome Incognito as a completely free (and approximate) alternative.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-12-semrush-simple-sign-up-account-keyword-and-ranking-research\">12. <a href=\"https://www.semrush.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Semrush SImple Sign Up Account</a>: Keyword and Ranking Research</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Semrush and Ahrefs are the industry standard for keyword, backlink, and ranking research.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can create a simple sign-up account that gives you access to a limited set of Semrush’s keyword research, PPC, and content marketing tools. Note: this differs from their <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">7-day free trial</a>: the simple sign-up account has <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">no time limit</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs offers a similar <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free plan for 1 domain</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-backlink-checkers-and-link-building\">Backlink Checkers and Link Building </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The following tools support backlink analysis and outreach for guest posting.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-13-hunter-io-find-hidden-contact-emails\">13. <a href=\"https://hunter.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Hunter.io</a>: Find Hidden Contact Emails</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hunter.io helps you find verified email addresses associated with a website, including for upper management. It’s notoriously good at this and a must-have for outreach.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For quick searches, use the free <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/hunter-email-finder-exten/hgmhmanijnjhaffoampdlllchpolkdnj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Hunter Email Finder</a> Chrome extension.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"883\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-1024x883.jpg\" alt=\"hunter chrome extension\" class=\"wp-image-234430\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-1024x883.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-300x259.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-768x662.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-600x517.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-70x60.jpg 70w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension-104x90.jpg 104w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunter-chrome-extension.jpg 1436w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-backlink-checker-from-neil-patel\">14. <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/backlinks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Backlink Checker from Neil Patel</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To use the free backlink checker at <strong>NeilPatel.com</strong>, enter a domain. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"433\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-1024x433.png\" alt=\"neil patel free backlink checker\" class=\"wp-image-235361\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-1024x433.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-300x127.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-768x325.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-1536x650.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-600x254.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-142x60.png 142w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel-213x90.png 213w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/backlink-checker-neil-patel.png 1678w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Youll be redirected to Ubersuggest: his full-featured keyword research tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There you&#8217;ll see a graph of backlink growth, total number of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\" title=\"\">referring domains and backlinks</a>, and a thorough analysis.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"516\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-1024x516.png\" alt=\"free ubersuggest backlink checker\" class=\"wp-image-235362\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-1024x516.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-768x387.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-1536x774.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-2048x1031.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-600x302.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubersuggest-backlink-checker-179x90.png 179w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: You&#8217;ll get 3 searches a day on the free plan. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Paid plans start at <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$29/month</a>. And Ubersuggest is offering new <strong>Lifetime deals</strong>, that offer significant savings over all competitors. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-ahrefs-free-backlink-checker\">15. <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/backlink-checker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs: Free Backlink Checker</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs also has a free backlink checker. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"469\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-1024x469.png\" alt=\"ahrefs free backlink checker\" class=\"wp-image-235367\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-1024x469.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-300x138.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-768x352.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-1536x704.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-600x275.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-131x60.png 131w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker-196x90.png 196w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlink-checker.png 1824w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter your domain and you&#8217;ll get basic stats and a limited list of backlinks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"838\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-1024x838.png\" alt=\"ahrefs free backlink checker interface\" class=\"wp-image-235368\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-1024x838.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-300x246.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-768x629.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-1536x1257.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-600x491.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-73x60.png 73w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker-110x90.png 110w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ahrefs-free-backlinks-checker.png 1664w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To view all the backlinks pointed to your domain you&#8217;ll need to sign up for an Ahrefs plan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-free-site-speed-checkers\">Best Free Site Speed Checkers</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Site loading speed can impact your ranking. Here we share 2 of the best free speed analysis tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep in mind that the recommendations that these tools make are technical, and you&#8217;ll need a developer to act on them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-14-google-pagespeed-insights-measure-and-improve\">16. <a href=\"https://pagespeed.web.dev/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google PageSpeed Insights</a>: Measure and Improve</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google PageSpeed Insights provides everything a coder needs to improve website performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With its trademark circular scores, PageSpeed Insights provides overall speed, performance, SEO, and accessibility ratings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can toggle between mobile and desktop reports.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"325\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-1024x325.png\" alt=\"google pagespeed insights scores\" class=\"wp-image-234431\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-1024x325.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-300x95.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-768x244.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-600x190.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-190x60.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores-284x90.png 284w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/google-pagespeed-insights-scores.png 1305w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Scroll down to the audit section to get detailed guidance on improvements.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-15-gtmetrix-detailed-performance-and-speed-reports\">17. <a href=\"https://gtmetrix.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">GTmetrix</a>: Detailed Performance and Speed Reports</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a URL to GTmetrix for a performance and structure grade and “Web Vitals” numbers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below those numbers is a wealth of information, including a waterfall chart and tabbed report with details.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"442\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-1024x442.jpg\" alt=\"gtmetrix scores\" class=\"wp-image-234434\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-1024x442.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-300x130.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-768x332.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-1536x663.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-2048x885.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-600x259.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-139x60.jpg 139w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gtmetrix-interface-208x90.jpg 208w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version of GTmetrix offers 25 weekly tests. Paid plans start at <a href=\"https://gtmetrix.com/pricing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$8.54/month</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-free-analytics-tools\">Best Free Analytics Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our last category of best free SEO tools are analytics software platforms.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Any of these tools can be used at the beginner or advanced level.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-16-google-search-console-see-your-rankings\">18. <a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google Search Console</a>: See Your Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Wondering how you’re ranking in Google Search for various keywords? You can find out with Google Search Console.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to ranking data and trends, you’ll get informed of any indexing issues or manual penalties. (As long as you protect your site from hacks and don’t do any black hat SEO, you shouldn’t worry about penalties from Google.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Good to know</strong>: All in One SEO (AIOSEO) includes Google Search Console data in its Search Statistics feature. This feature is available in the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Elite version</a> of the plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-1024x830.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo seo statistics feature\" class=\"wp-image-226990\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-1024x830.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-300x243.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-768x622.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-600x486.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-74x60.jpg 74w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics-111x90.jpg 111w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-seo-statistics.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: A view of the Google Search Console integration available in All in One SEO (AIOSEO).</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-17-google-analytics-website-results\">19. <a href=\"https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/provision/#/provision\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google Analytics</a>: Website Results</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Analytics provides an amazing amount of data. In addition to the standard page views and traffic information, you can use it to track sales funnels and e-commerce data so you know which pages and marketing tactics are working best.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Good to know</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">MonsterInsights</a> is a WordPress plugin that pulls Google Analytics data into simple visual displays in the WordPress editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-18-looker-studio-data-visualization-and-reports\">20. <a href=\"https://lookerstudio.google.com/u/0/navigation/reporting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Looker Studio</a>: Data Visualization and Reports</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Looker Studio is Google’s rebrand of Data Studio. It’s used to create dashboards and custom reports from website data.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"448\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-1024x448.png\" alt=\"google looker studio interface\" class=\"wp-image-234436\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-1024x448.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-300x131.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-768x336.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-1536x672.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-2048x896.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-600x263.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-137x60.png 137w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/looker-studio-example-206x90.png 206w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Above: This is a closeup of a Looker Studio report, presenting data from Google Search Console.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-19-screaming-frog-seo-spider-detailed-link-analysis\">21. <a href=\"https://www.screamingfrog.co.uk/seo-spider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Screaming Frog SEO Spider</a>: Detailed Link Analysis</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Screaming Frog SEO Spider is a site audit tool popular with web developers, designers, and marketers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It thoroughly analyzes every single link in a website and highlights problems like duplicate content and broken links.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"674\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-1024x674.jpg\" alt=\"screaming frog seo spider interface\" class=\"wp-image-196376\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-1024x674.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-300x197.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-768x505.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-1536x1010.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-600x395.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-91x60.jpg 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-137x90.jpg 137w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard.jpg 2028w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-bonus-tools\">Bonus Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/webmasters/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"><strong>Bing Webmaster Tools</strong></a> is Bing’s version of Google Search Console. It’s a good idea to create an account for it to get insights into your performance in Bing search results.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Mozbar</strong> from Moz.com is an SEO toolbar available for free from the <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/mozbar/eakacpaijcpapndcfffdgphdiccmpknp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Chrome web store</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>While you’re working on SEO, get ready to maximize conversions. Our favorite tools for this are <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">OptinMonster</a> and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">WPForms</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-qa-on-free-seo-tools\">Q&amp;A on Best Free SEO Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-do-seo-for-free\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">How do I do SEO for free?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>To do SEO for free, we recommend using a WordPress plugin like All in One SEO (AIOSEO). There&#8217;s a free version of the plugin, called AIOSEO Lite, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">available on WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO will analyze your pages for you and tell you how to improve your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, follow this blog and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube channel</a> to learn more about SEO.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-does-google-have-a-free-seo-tool\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Does Google have a free SEO tool?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Google offers several free tools that are <em>support</em> SEO decision-making: Google Analytics, Google Search Console, and Google PageSpeed Insights.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-resources-on-seo-tools\">Resources on SEO Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/yoast-vs-rank-math-vs-all-in-one-seo/\" title=\"\">Yoast vs Rank Math vs All in One SEO: Which Is Better?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/yoast-seo-vs-all-in-one-seo-which-is-the-best-seo-plugin/\" title=\"\">Yoast SEO vs All in One SEO: Which Is the Best SEO Plugin?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/migrating-from-yoast-seo-to-all-in-one-seo/\" title=\"\">Migrating From Yoast SEO to All in One SEO (2 Simple Steps)</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\" title=\"\">The 9 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-on-page-seo-tools/\" title=\"\">Best On-Page SEO Tools for WordPress (Tested and Reviewed)</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\" title=\"\">9 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-rank-tracker/\" title=\"\">The Best SEO Rank Tracker: 6 Fantastic Tools to Help You Dominate the SERPs</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-schema-generator-plugins/\" title=\"\">6 Best WordPress Schema Generator Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find some of the best free SEO tools to rank higher.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, explore our review of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\">best WordPress SEO plugins</a> and the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-on-page-seo-tools/\">best on-page SEO tools</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find plenty of WordPress tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-seo-tools/\">21 Best Free SEO Tools to Boost Your Rankings</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-seo-tools/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"7 Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses (And Pro Tips)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:136:\"https://aioseo.com/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://aioseo.com/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 11 Oct 2023 13:17:09 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"benefits of SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"SEO tips for small businesses\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"small business SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=229013\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:455:\"<p>Would you like to know the benefits of SEO for small businesses? Search engine optimization (SEO) is a powerful digital marketing strategy to help your website and business become more visible to online searchers. This makes it an excellent channel&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses/\">7 Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses (And Pro Tips)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20810:\"<p>Would you like to know the benefits of SEO for small businesses?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Search engine optimization (SEO) is a powerful digital marketing strategy to help your website and business become more visible to online searchers. This makes it an excellent channel for marketing your business and products, even if you’re a small business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you the benefits of SEO for small businesses.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-seo\">What is SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses\">7 Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-increased-visibility-on-serps\">1. Increased Visibility on SERPs</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-boosts-brand-awareness\">2. Boosts Brand Awareness</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-drives-sales\">3. Drives Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-cost-effective-marketing-channel\">4. Cost-effective Marketing Channel</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-powerful-lead-generation-strategy\">5. Powerful Lead Generation Strategy</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-helps-build-credibility-and-authority\">6. Helps Build Credibility and Authority</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-can-help-drive-local-traffic\">7. Can Help Drive Local Traffic</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-cons-of-seo-for-small-businesses\">The Cons of SEO for Small Businesses</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-your-faqs-answered\">Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-is-seo-important-for-small-businesses\">Why is SEO important for small businesses?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-the-key-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses\">What are the key benefits of SEO for small businesses?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-the-best-seo-tools-for-small-businesses\">What are the best SEO tools for small businesses?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-the-effort-is-well-worth-it\">The Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses: The Effort is Well Worth It!</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-seo\">What is SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the process of optimizing a site or its content to improve its ranking and visibility in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs). The primary goals of SEO include making it easier for search engines to crawl, understand, and rank your site or content for relevant search queries. Doing so results in more people finding your content when they search online, leading to more organic traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This brings us to our main discussion of the day: the benefits of SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses\">7 Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many pros and cons of SEO for small businesses. In this section, we’ll focus on the pros/benefits.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, let’s get to it!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-increased-visibility-on-serps\">1. Increased Visibility on SERPs</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most significant benefits of SEO is that it increases your visibility on SERPs. Visibility on SERPs is crucial as there’s a lot of competition on SERPs. For example, take a look at the screenshot below. It shows how many <a href=\"https://www.worldometers.info/blogs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">blog posts were written today</a> (as of the writing of this article):</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ASnOsjQKOitkBBFrluzT__7_HoBksHe7meLAp8aMTvJAVhC58p-7JMlABcXUlp7rAbm132wBQZAubCrfKpf4RzMjqJ1rGOCvGNn6valdxqTuqQQlQrDOJw97_H8CK4kQ-B__8-qwIksmIK7P2j0f_VI\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With so much competition, getting eyes on your content is very important. And SEO does just that, especially if you have the best WordPress SEO plugins. And it doesn’t get any better than <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and is trusted by over 3 million savvy website owners and marketers to help them dominate the SERPs and drive relevant traffic to their sites. This is because the plugin has many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">powerful SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users. Examples of said features include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search Statistics:</strong> This powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/search-statistics/\" title=\"Search Statistics\">Google Search Console integration</a> lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>AI Title/Description Generator</strong>: An AI-powered tool that generates SEO titles and meta descriptions with 1-click.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Next-gen Schema Generator</strong>: This makes adding any type of schema markup super easy.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Redirection Manager</strong>: Helps you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\" title=\"Redirection Manager\">manage redirects</a> and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and index your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Link Assistant</strong>: Powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">internal linking tool</a> that automates building links between pages on your site. It also gives you an audit of outbound links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>SEO Preview</strong>: The <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\" title=\"What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?\">SEO Preview tool</a> gives you an overview of your search and social snippets and general SEO so you can improve your optimization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>IndexNow:</strong> For <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/indexnow/\" title=\"IndexNow\">instantaneous indexing</a> on search engines that support the IndexNow protocol (like Bing and Yandex).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Robots.txt editor</strong>: The <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">advanced Robots.txt editor</a> gives you full control over the instructions you give web crawlers about what folders and files to crawl on your WordPress site.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>All these features (and more) help boost your site’s visibility on SERPs. Others also help you boost your organic clickthrough rate. This, too, boosts your visibility and also results in business growth.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-boosts-brand-awareness\">2. Boosts Brand Awareness</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another benefit of SEO for small businesses is that it can help increase brand awareness. Brand awareness refers to the extent of your target audience&#8217;s familiarity with your brand and how easily they can recognize it. This is critical to business growth. The more familiar people are with your brand, the more likely they will do business with you.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO helps boost your brand awareness because the more your content ranks high on search engines, the more touchpoints your prospects have with your brand. Touchpoints simply refer to the encounters your prospects have with your brand. SEO gives you a lot of opportunities to get your site, products, and other content in front of your target audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-drives-sales\">3. Drives Sales</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most benefits of SEO have a snowball effect, particularly the benefit of high-quality traffic. High-quality traffic leads to high-quality leads, leading to a boost in sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because SEO’s primary goal is to help you become more discoverable by your target audience, ranking high means reaching more people interested in your product or services. And if you play your SEO cards right, you may even <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-featured-snippets-on-google/\" title=\"How to Get Featured Snippets on Google [A Beginners Guide]\">land the featured snippet</a>, also called position zero. This is usually the first organic ranking after ads and gets more real estate on SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-get-featured-snippets-1.png\" alt=\"Example of snippets on search engine results pages.\" class=\"wp-image-235333\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-get-featured-snippets-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-get-featured-snippets-1-300x228.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-get-featured-snippets-1-600x456.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting to the top of the SERPs results in you getting a whopping <a href=\"https://backlinko.com/google-ctr-stats\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">27.6% of all clicks</a> on the top page of SERPs. This means you get the lion&#8217;s share of traffic. It also means you generate more sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-cost-effective-marketing-channel\">4. Cost-effective Marketing Channel</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most small businesses and startups don’t have the luxury of massive marketing budgets. And that’s why SEO must be one of your top marketing channels. That’s because not only is it effective, but it is also cost-effective compared to other marketing channels like paid advertising.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One way in which SEO can help you save money is that you can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-boost-your-small-business-seo/\" title=\"How to Boost Your Small Business SEO Without Expert Help\">DIY your SEO</a>. With the right SEO tools and plugins, you can easily design, develop, and deploy your campaigns without hiring an SEO specialist.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another factor that makes SEO cost-effective is that it continues to bring results for years. Sure, you may need to do some maintenance work on your site and content regularly, but each campaign will continue bringing you traffic without you having to spend another cent. This means you get a high return on investment despite not having spent much.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-powerful-lead-generation-strategy\">5. Powerful Lead Generation Strategy</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Leads are the lifeblood of any business, especially small businesses looking to break into a competitive market.  That’s why a well-executed SEO campaign results in you driving targeted traffic to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This targeted traffic is more likely to convert into paid customers than traffic from paid campaigns, as inbound leads come to your site by choice. Your content attracts them because they find it valuable. As a result, they’re more likely to convert into paying customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason SEO is such a powerful lead generation strategy is that people prefer organic results on search engines to paid ads. That’s why <a href=\"https://videos.brightedge.com/research-report/BrightEdge_ChannelReport2019_FINAL.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">68% of all online experiences</a> start with a search engine. And that’s also why organic search results convert better.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-6-helps-build-credibility-and-authority\">6. Helps Build Credibility and Authority</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ranking high on search engines signals to users that your brand is credible enough to be trusted by search engines. In addition, seeing your brand and content on the first page of SERPs instills a sense of trust in your target audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides helping build credibility, SEO helps you establish yourself as an authority in your field. The more people find your content, the more they deem you an authority in your niche.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both these aspects of SEO can be bolstered further, not just by ranking high on SERPs but also by having your search listing show social proof.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And what better social proof than reviews?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is why you need a powerful SEO tool like AIOSEO. It makes it easy to add any type of schema to your site and content, with review schema being one of them.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"264\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-review.png\" alt=\"Example of reviews on SERPs.\" class=\"wp-image-235348\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-review.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-review-300x113.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-review-600x226.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can check out our guide on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Add Product Review Schema in WordPress\">adding review schema here</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A well-executed SEO strategy will benefit your business by helping you build credibility and authority. And these are essential ingredients for growing a thriving business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-can-help-drive-local-traffic\">7. Can Help Drive Local Traffic</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you run a service-based business or brick-and-mortar establishment, your target audience is within your geographical location. Because of this, it may be tempting to think you don’t need to invest that much into SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the contrary, you still need SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/12-local-seo-stats-every-business-owner-and-marketer-should-know-in-2019-i/549079/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Research shows</a> that 46% of all searches on Google have local intent. It also shows that 97% of search engine users have searched for a local business online.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Especially if you’re a local business, you need SEO to make it easy for your customers to find your business. For example, you can add Local Business schema to help search engines identify your business and service area.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-embed-google-maps-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Embed Google Maps in WordPress\">embed Google Maps</a> in your content to make it easier for your customers to find your location.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"367\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/embed-google-maps-in-wordpress-final.png\" alt=\"Embedding Google Maps in WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-161593\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/embed-google-maps-in-wordpress-final.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/embed-google-maps-in-wordpress-final-300x157.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/embed-google-maps-in-wordpress-final-600x314.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/embed-google-maps-in-wordpress-final-115x60.png 115w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/embed-google-maps-in-wordpress-final-172x90.png 172w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All these make it super easy for you to rank for local searches and drive traffic to your site and business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-cons-of-seo-for-small-businesses\">The Cons of SEO for Small Businesses</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While SEO is one of the best marketing channels for small businesses, it also has its caveats, although only a few. One of the most significant cons of SEO for small businesses is that it can take time for you to start seeing results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, to combat this problem, you can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-indexnow-for-seo/\" title=\"What is IndexNow for SEO (Explained in Plain English)?\">use our IndexNow module</a> to get your content indexed faster on platforms that support the IndexNow protocol.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The other significant con of SEO is that search engines are always changing and improving their algorithms. However, if your SEO strategy follows search engine guidelines, these won’t impact your rankings and traffic that much.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, when you consider the pros and cons of SEO, it’s evident that the pros far outweigh the cons.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-your-faqs-answered\">Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-is-seo-important-for-small-businesses\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Why is SEO important for small businesses?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO is crucial for small businesses because it helps increase their online visibility, attract more organic traffic, and compete with larger competitors. It&#8217;s a cost-effective way to reach a wider audience.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-the-key-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are the key benefits of SEO for small businesses?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Some key benefits of SEO for small businesses include increased website traffic, improved online visibility, higher conversion rates, and better brand recognition.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-the-best-seo-tools-for-small-businesses\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are the best SEO tools for small businesses?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The best SEO tool for small businesses is AIOSEO because it lets you DIY your SEO. It also has many features to help you rank your site on search engines.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses-the-effort-is-well-worth-it\">The Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses: The Effort is Well Worth It!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO should be your primary marketing channel if you’re a small business or startup. This is because it can give you a lot of mileage even on a small budget. Plus, if you have a powerful SEO plugin like AIOSEO, you can even DIY your SEO and manage to compete with the bigger brands in your industry.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you know the main benefits of SEO for small businesses. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-start-a-small-business-blog/\" title=\"How to Start a Small Business Blog in 2023\">how to start a small business blog</a> and our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/blog-post-seo-checklist/\" title=\"A Complete Blog Post SEO Checklist to Boost Rankings\">blog post SEO checklist</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (formerly Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses/\">7 Benefits of SEO for Small Businesses (And Pro Tips)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://aioseo.com/benefits-of-seo-for-small-businesses/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1: