\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wpcharitable.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"WP Charitable\">WP Charitable</a> is the best WordPress donations plugin on the market. The plugin was designed to make it easy for you to collect donations on your WordPress site. And users love it because, unlike most donation platforms, WP Charitable has $0 transaction fees (on paid plans)!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your business depends wholly or partly on donations, WP Charitable should be on your list of the best WooCommerce alternatives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason is that charitable marketing is one of the best ways to boost sales and grow a committed customer base. <a href=\"https://www.pymnts.com/buy-now-pay-later/2020/how-charitable-giving-boosts-online-bnpl-sales-customer-engagement/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Studies show</a> that partnering with charity organizations can help boost your sales and reduce your churn rate.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ease-of-use is another strong suit WP Charitable users love. Thanks to its library of donation forms, you can set up campaigns with just a few clicks. The forms are highly customizable, can be tweaked to match your theme, and only include the form fields you want, among many other customizations. Plus, all donation form templates are GDPR-ready.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And the best part is that you can create and manage all your campaigns right from your WordPress dashboard.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All these and more reasons make WP Charitable the best WooCommerce alternative for brands that accept donations on their WordPress sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $99/year. A free plan is also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-wpforms\">7. <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms - Drag &amp; Drop WordPress Form Builder\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"435\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms.png\" alt=\"WP Forms homepage\" class=\"wp-image-128844\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms-300x186.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms-600x373.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms - Drag &amp; Drop WordPress Form Builder\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> is the world’s best form builder plugin and boasts over 5 million users. You can use it to add any form on your site, making it easier to generate leads, run surveys, register people for events, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a WooCommerce alternative, WPForms offers a simple, straightforward way of accepting payments on your WordPress site. This is thanks to the powerful order forms it enables you to create. WPForms is a solid solution if you don’t need a complete shopping cart or checkout system to sell on your site. It’s the perfect eCommerce solution if you sell a single product or service to sell.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Online billing &amp; order forms</li>\n\n\n\n<li>400+ templates</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drag-and-drop form builder</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Support for multiple payment gateways (Stripe, PayPal, Square)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recurring subscriptions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>User journey tracking</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. However, you’ll need a Pro license ($159.60 annually) to accept payments through your forms.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-8-smash-balloon-instagram-feeds\">8. <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Smashballoon Instagram Feeds\">Smash Balloon Instagram Feeds</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-woocommerce-alternatives-smash-balloon.png\" alt=\"Smashballoon Instagram Feeds homepage\" class=\"wp-image-228997\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-woocommerce-alternatives-smash-balloon.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-woocommerce-alternatives-smash-balloon-300x162.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-woocommerce-alternatives-smash-balloon-600x323.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another WordPress plugin you can consider when looking for WooCommerce alternatives is <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Smashballoon Instagram Feeds\">Smashballoon’s Instagram Feed Pro</a>. Smashballoon is a powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-social-media-plugins-for-wordpress-compared/\" title=\"The 7 Best Social Media Plugins for WordPress (Compared)\">social media feed plugin for WordPress</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instagram Feed Pro allows you to add Instagram feeds to your site. And if you sell products on your site, you can use it to set up shoppable Instagram feeds on your WordPress website. A shoppable Instagram feed allows you to tag your products in photos you post. However, shoppable feeds are only available for physical products.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using Instagram Feed Pro, you can easily showcase a shoppable Instagram gallery like this on your site:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"496\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-woocommerce-alternatives-smashballoon-1.jpg\" alt=\"example of smashballoon gallery.